2, \"to\": 3195}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At China's national diving championships in November 2023, upset fans believed that judges had under-scored Quan Hongchan, who came in second to teammate Chen Yuxi, and Chen's family was subject to online abuse.\", \"from\": 3198, \"to\": 3409, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3201, \"end\": 3206, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9999981513100273, \"rank\": 1.7188565826678292e-06, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}, {\"begin\": 3352, \"end\": 3361, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chen_Yuxi\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Chen Yuxi\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chen_Yuxi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chen_Yuxi\"}, {\"begin\": 3367, \"end\": 3371, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chen_Shui-bian\", \"score\": 0.9999766117118523, \"rank\": 2.3359614318260566e-05, \"text\": \"Chen\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chen_Shui-bian\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chen_Shui-bian\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"November\", \"from\": 3242, \"to\": 3250}, {\"ngram\": \"upset fans\", \"from\": 3257, \"to\": 3267}, {\"ngram\": \"judges\", \"from\": 3282, \"to\": 3288}, {\"ngram\": \"under-scored Quan Hongchan\", \"from\": 3293, \"to\": 3319}, {\"ngram\": \"online abuse\", \"from\": 3396, \"to\": 3408}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Mr Adam Zhang, founder of Chinese sports consultancy firmKey-Solution, said that there is a need to differentiate between normal fan behaviour and those that need to be addressed.\", \"from\": 3411, \"to\": 3590, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3437, \"end\": 3444, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\", \"score\": 0.9650935395265409, \"rank\": 0.03592158159591428, \